data.description: Country Living in this Custom 2 1/2 story Home on 2 Acres in Summerwood has never sounded so nice! This 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath also features a 3rd floor flex room. This house is absolutely stunning inside and out, with a covered wrap-around front porch on the main home and beautiful interior finishes, this is a must see! New Roof, windows, renovated bathrooms and luxury flooring! A Lovely Gourmet Kitchen, Spacious Laundry Rm, Propane FP, Heat Pump/AC, Generator Hookup, Central Vac & Sprinkler Systems are just some of the many highlights of this Amazing Property. Additional Detached 3 Car Garage/Barn/Shop includes Full bath, laundry area, 2nd floor Finished 624 sqft ADU, a Stable w/2 stalls & a fenced pasture! This Property is ALL THAT & MORE!!!
